otpointercapture = <var>functionRef</var>;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"値","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code><var>functionRef</var></code> は、関数名または<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/function\">関数式</a>です。 関数は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent\"><code>PointerEvent</code></a> オブジェクトを唯一の引数として受け取ります。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">overHandler</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// ターゲットイベントの gotpointercapture ハンドラを決定します</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> gotCaptureHandler <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ongotpointercapture<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> el <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'target'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  el<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ongotpointercapture <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> overHandler<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/pointerevents2/#the-gotpointercapture-event\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Pointer Events – Level 2<br><small lang=\"ja\">ongotpointercapture の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.GlobalEventHandlers.ongotpointercapture","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/ongotpointercapture/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Document/gotpointercapture_event\">Document: gotpointercapture</a></code> イベント</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/gotpointercapture_event\">HTMLElement: gotpointercapture</a></code> イベント</li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element/setPointerCapture\"><code>Element.setPointerCapture()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specification"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"ongotpointercapture は GlobalEventHandlers ミックスインのプロパティで、 gotpointercapture イベントを処理する event handler です。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.ongotpointercapture","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Element.ongotpointercapture","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.ongotpointercapture","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.on